---
title: Caribbean Kidney Bean & Coconut Soup with Roasted Veggies
description: One good way to beat the chill? Channel the flavours of the Caribbean into a hearty soup with kidney beans and roasted kumara.
Chilli, coconut and Caribbean spices bring a summery warmth that'll make you feel toasty inside.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-kidney-bean-coconut-soup-d7f859a1.jpg
